<h1>Dice Game</h1>
Here are the rules
<ul>
<li>Roll the dice to start the game</li>
<li>If your first roll is a 7 or 11, you win</li>
<li>If your first roll is a 2, 3, or 12, you lose</li>
<li>Anything else becomes your <i>goal</i>. Roll your goal again before getting a 7, and you win. Roll a 7 instead of your goal, and you lose</li></ul>
<form action="/dice/roll">
<button>Roll Dice</button>
</form>